data.description:
4 Bedroom 2.1 Bath Home for Sale in Western Oklahoma.  Handy Man Special! Roll up your sleeves and add the touches YOU want to make this home your own!  Home is sitting on 4 acres MOL with 2 barns and corals with fencing.  Vinyl tilt in windows throughout the home.    Feel safe with the underground storm shelter and enjoy the backyard with mature trees and a large concrete patio.  Shop is 22 x 24 with a concrete floor and shed with coral is 53 x 21, partially enclosed.  Close to town but with all the luxury of living in the country.  Merritt School District. 
 Home has so much potential it is just waiting for a new family to call it HOME!
